56/*
57 * 'full' is zero for a 'diff' dump, so things like symbol numbers,
58 * ili numbers, etc., are left off; this makes ili trees and symbol dumps
59 * that are for all intents and purposes the same look more identical.
60 * 'full' is 2 for an 'important things' only dump; nmptr, hashlk left off
61 * 'full' is 1 for full dump, everything
62 */
63static int full = 1;

89static void
90putit(void)
91{
92 int l = strlen(BUF);
93 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
94 if (linelen + l >= 78 && !longlines) {
95 fprintf(dfile, "\n%s", BUF);
96 linelen = l;
97 } else if (linelen > 0 && nexttight) {
98 fprintf(dfile, "%s", BUF);
99 linelen += l + 1;
100 } else if (linelen > 0 && tight) {
101 fprintf(dfile, " %s", BUF);
102 linelen += l + 1;
103 } else if (linelen > 0) {
104 fprintf(dfile, " %s", BUF);
105 linelen += l + 2;
106 } else {
107 fprintf(dfile, "%s", BUF);
108 linelen = l;
109 }
110 nexttight = 0;
111} /* putit */
112

114puttight(void)

119 linelen += l;
120} /* puttight */

139static void
140puterr(const char *fmt, ...)
141{
142 va_list argptr;
143 va_start(argptr, fmt);
144 putline();
145 strcpy(BUF, "*** ");
146 vsnprintf(BUF + 4, BUFSIZE - 4, fmt, argptr);
147 strcat(BUF, " ***");
148 putit();
149 putline();
150} /* puterr */

350static void
351putdefarray(const char *s, char **arr)
352{
353 int i;
354 if (arr != NULL) {
355 for (i = 0; arr[i] != NULL; i += 2) {
356 if (arr[i + 1] == (const char *)1) {
357 snprintf(BUF, BUFSIZE, "%s[%d] pred:%s", s, i, arr[i]);
358 } else if (arr[i + 1] == (const char *)0) {
359 snprintf(BUF, BUFSIZE, "%s[%d] undef:%s", s, i, arr[i]);
360 } else {
361 snprintf(BUF, BUFSIZE, "%s[%d] def:%s", s, i, arr[i]);
362 }
363 putit();
364 putline();
365 }
366 }
367} /* putdefarray */

398static void
399putsym(const char *s, SPTR sptr)
400{
401 if (full) {
402 if (sptr == NOSYM) {
403 snprintf(BUF, BUFSIZE, "%s:%d=%s", s, sptr, "NOSYM");
404 } else if (sptr > 0 && sptr < stb.stg_avail) {
405 snprintf(BUF, BUFSIZE, "%s:%d=%s%s", s, sptr, printname(sptr),
406 ADDRTKNG(sptr) ? " (&)" : "");
407 } else {
408 snprintf(BUF, BUFSIZE, "%s:%d", s, sptr);
409 }
410 } else {
411 if (sptr == NOSYM) {
412 snprintf(BUF, BUFSIZE, "%s:%s", s, "NOSYM");
413 } else if (sptr > 0 && sptr < stb.stg_avail) {
414 snprintf(BUF, BUFSIZE, "%s:%s%s", s, printname(sptr),
415 ADDRTKNG(sptr) ? " (&)" : "");
416 } else {
417 snprintf(BUF, BUFSIZE, "%s:%d", s, sptr);
418 }
419 }
420
421 putit();
422} /* putsym */

532static void
533putsymlk(const char *name, int list)
534{
535 int c = 0;
536 if (list <= NOSYM)
537 return;
538 putline();
539 putstring1(name);
540 for (; list > NOSYM && c < 200; list = SYMLKG(list), ++c)
541 putsym1(list);
542 putline();
543} /* putsymlk */

545void
546putnme(const char *s, int nme)
547{
548 if (full) {
549 if (nme < 0 || nme >= nmeb.stg_avail) {
550 snprintf(BUF, BUFSIZE, "%s:%d=%s", s, nme, "NONE");
551 putit();
552 } else {
553 snprintf(BUF, BUFSIZE, "%s:%d=", s, nme);
554 putit();
555 _printnme(nme);
556 }
557 } else {
558 if (nme < 0 || nme >= nmeb.stg_avail) {
559 snprintf(BUF, BUFSIZE, "%s:%d", s, nme);
560 putit();
561 } else {
562 snprintf(BUF, BUFSIZE, "%s:", s);
563 putit();
564 _printnme(nme);
565 }
566 }
567} /* putnme */

601#ifdef SOCPTRG
602void
603putsoc(int socptr)
604{
605 int p, q;
606
607 if (socptr == 0)
608 return;
609 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
610 if (soc.base == NULL) {
611 fprintf(dfile, "soc.base not allocated\n");
612 return;
613 }
614 q = 0;
615 putline();
616 putstring1("Storage Overlap Chain:");
617
618 for (p = socptr; p; p = SOC_NEXT(p)) {
619 putsym1(SOC_SPTR(p));
620 if (q == p) {
621 putstring1(" >>> soc loop");
622 break;
623 }
624 q = p;
625 }
626} /* putsoc */
627#endif /* SOCPTRG */

630static void
631putcuda(const char *s, int cu)
632{
633 if (cu) {
634 strcpy(BUF, s);
635 strcat(BUF, ":");
636 if (cu & CUDA_HOST) {
637 strcat(BUF, "host");
638 cu &= ~CUDA_HOST;
639 if (cu)
640 strcat(BUF, "+");
641 }
642 if (cu & CUDA_DEVICE) {
643 strcat(BUF, "device");
644 cu &= ~CUDA_DEVICE;
645 if (cu)
646 strcat(BUF, "+");
647 }
648 if (cu & CUDA_GLOBAL) {
649 strcat(BUF, "global");
650 cu &= ~CUDA_GLOBAL;
651 if (cu)
652 strcat(BUF, "+");
653 }
654 if (cu & CUDA_BUILTIN) {
655 strcat(BUF, "builtin");
656 cu &= ~CUDA_BUILTIN;
657 if (cu)
658 strcat(BUF, "+");
659 }
660 if (cu & CUDA_CONSTRUCTOR) {
661 strcat(BUF, "constructor");
662 cu &= ~CUDA_CONSTRUCTOR;
663 if (cu)
664 strcat(BUF, "+");
665 }
666#ifdef CUDA_STUB
667 if (cu & CUDA_STUB) {
668 strcat(BUF, "stub");
669 cu &= ~CUDA_STUB;
670 if (cu)
671 strcat(BUF, "+");
672 }
673#endif
674 putit();
675 }
676} /* putcuda */
677#endif

687/* dump one symbol to gbl.dbgfil */
688void
689dsym(int sptr)
690{
691 SYMTYPE stype;
692 DTYPE dtype;
693 const char *np;
694#ifdef SOCPTRG
695 int socptr;
696#endif
697 int i;
698
699 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
700
701 if (sptr == 0 || sptr >= stb.stg_avail) {
702 fprintf(dfile, "\nsymbol %d out of %d\n", sptr, stb.stg_avail - 1);
703 return;
704 }
705
706 BCOPY(stb.stg_base, stb.stg_base + sptr, SYM, 1);
707
708 stype = STYPEG(0);
709 switch (stype) {
710 case ST_BLOCK:
711 case ST_CMBLK:
712 case ST_LABEL:
713 case ST_BASE:
714 case ST_UNKNOWN:
715 dtype = DT_NONE;
716 break;
717 default:
718 dtype = DTYPEG(0);
719 break;
720 }
721 np = printname(sptr);
722 if (strlen(np) >= 30) {
723 fprintf(dfile, "\n%s", np);
724 np = " ";
725 }
726 fprintf(dfile, "\n%-30.30s ", np);
727 if (dtype) {
728 putdtypex(dtype, 50);
729 }
730 fprintf(dfile, "\n");
731
732 linelen = 0;
733
734 if (full) {
735 putint("sptr", sptr);
736 putnzint("dtype", DTYPEG(0));
737 }
738 if (full & 1)
739 putnzint("nmptr", NMPTRG(0));
740 putnsc("sc", SCG(0));
741 putstype("stype", STYPEG(0));
742 putline();
743 STYPEP(0, ST_UNKNOWN);
744 DTYPEP(0, DT_NONE);
745 NMPTRP(0, 0);
746 SCP(0, SC_NONE);
747
748 if (full & 1)
749 putnsym("hashlk", HASHLKG(0));
750 putnsym("scope", SCOPEG(SPTR_NULL));
751 putnsym("symlk", SYMLKG(0));
752 putline();
753 HASHLKP(0, SPTR_NULL);
754 SCOPEP(0, 0);
755 SYMLKP(0, SPTR_NULL);
756
757 switch (stype) {
758 default:
759 break;
760 case ST_ARRAY:
761 case ST_IDENT:
762 case ST_STRUCT:
763 case ST_UNION:
764 case ST_UNKNOWN:
765 case ST_VAR:
766 /* three lines: integers, symbols, bits */
767 putnzint("address", ADDRESSG(0));
768 ADDRESSP(0, 0);
769#ifdef SDSCG
770 putnsym("sdsc", SDSCG(0));
771 SDSCP(0, 0);
772#endif
773#ifdef ENCLFUNCG
774 putnsym("enclfunc", ENCLFUNCG(0));
775 ENCLFUNCP(0, 0);
776#endif
777#ifdef OMPACCDEVSYMG
778 putbit("ompaccel", OMPACCDEVSYMG(0));
779 OMPACCDEVSYMP(0, 0);
780#endif
781#ifdef OMPACCSHMEMG
782 putbit("ompaccel-shared", OMPACCSHMEMG(0));
783 OMPACCSHMEMP(0, 0);
784#endif
785#ifdef OMPACCSTRUCTG
786 putbit("ompaccel-host", OMPACCSTRUCTG(0));
787 OMPACCSTRUCTP(0, 0);
788#endif
789#ifdef OMPACCDEVSYMG
790 putbit("ompaccel", OMPACCDEVSYMG(0));
791 OMPACCDEVSYMP(0, 0);
792#endif
793#ifdef OMPACCSHMEMG
794 putbit("ompaccel-shared", OMPACCSHMEMG(0));
795 OMPACCSHMEMP(0, 0);
796#endif
797#ifdef OMPACCSTRUCTG
798 putbit("ompaccel-host", OMPACCSTRUCTG(0));
799 OMPACCSTRUCTP(0, 0);
800#endif
801#ifdef OMPACCLITERALG
802 putbit("ompaccel-literal", OMPACCLITERALG(0));
803 OMPACCLITERALP(0, 0);
804#endif
805#ifdef SOCPTRG
806 socptr = SOCPTRG(0);
807 putnzint("socptr", SOCPTRG(0));
808 SOCPTRP(0, 0);
809#endif
810 putline();
811 {
812#ifdef MDG
813 putmd("mdg", MDG(0));
814 MDP(0, 0);
815#endif
816 }
817 putnzint("b3", b3G(0));
818 b3P(0, 0);
819#ifdef ALIASG
820 putnsym("alias", ALIASG(0));
821 ALIASP(0, 0);
822#endif
823#ifdef ALTNAMEG
824 putnsym("altname", ALTNAMEG(0));
825 ALTNAMEP(0, 0);
826#endif
827#ifdef BASESYMG
828 if (BASEADDRG(0)) {
829 putnsym("basesym", BASESYMG(0));
830 BASESYMP(0, 0);
831 }

2091void
2092dsyms(int l, int u)
2093{
2094 int i;
2095 if (l <= 0)
2096 l = stb.firstusym;
2097 if (u <= 0)
2098 u = stb.stg_avail - 1;
2099 if (u >= stb.stg_avail)
2100 u = stb.stg_avail - 1;
2101 for (i = l; i <= u; ++i) {
2102 dsym(i);
2103 }
2104 fprintf(dfile, "\n");
2105} /* dsyms */

2377static bool
2378simpledtype(DTYPE dtype)
2379{
2380 if (dtype < DT_NONE || ((int)dtype) >= stb.dt.stg_avail)
2381 return false;
2382 if (DTY(dtype) < TY_NONE || DTY(dtype) > TY_MAX)
2383 return false;
2384 if (dlen(DTY(dtype)) == 1)
2385 return true;
2386 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_PTR)
2387 return true;
2388 return false;
2389} /* simpledtype */

2530void
2531_putdtype(DTYPE dtype, int structdepth)
2532{
2533 TY_KIND dty;
2534 ADSC *ad;
2535 int numdim;
2536 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
2537 if (dtype >= stb.dt.stg_avail) {
2538 fprintf(dfile, "\ndtype %d out of %d\n", dtype, stb.dt.stg_avail - 1);
2539 return;
2540 }
2541 dty = DTY(dtype);
2542 switch (dty) {
2543 default:
2544 putdty(dty);
2545 break;
2546 case TY_CHAR:
2547 appendstring1("char*");
2548 appendint1(DTyCharLength(dtype));
2549 break;
2550 case TY_ARRAY:
2551 _putdtype(DTySeqTyElement(dtype), structdepth);
2552 ad = AD_DPTR(dtype);
2553 numdim = AD_NUMDIM(ad);
2554 appendstring1("(");
2555 if (numdim >= 1 && numdim <= 7) {
2556 int i;
2557 for (i = 0; i < numdim; ++i) {
2558 if (i)
2559 appendstring1(",");
2560 appendsym1(AD_LWBD(ad, i));
2561 appendstring1(":");
2562 appendsym1(AD_UPBD(ad, i));
2563 }
2564 }
2565 appendstring1(")");
2566 break;
2567 case TY_PTR:
2568 if (simpledtype(DTySeqTyElement(dtype))) {
2569 appendstring1("*");
2570 _putdtype(DTySeqTyElement(dtype), structdepth);
2571 } else {
2572 appendstring1("*(");
2573 _putdtype(DTySeqTyElement(dtype), structdepth);
2574 appendstring1(")");
2575 }
2576 break;
2577 case TY_PARAM:
2578 appendstring1("(");
2579 _putdtype(DTyArgType(dtype), structdepth);
2580 if (DTyArgSym(dtype)) {
2581 appendstring1(" ");
2582 appendsym1(DTyArgSym(dtype));
2583 }
2584 if (DTyArgNext(dtype)) {
2585 appendstring1(", next=");
2586 appendint1(DTyArgNext(dtype));
2587 }
2588 appendstring1(")");
2589 break;
2590 case TY_STRUCT:
2591 case TY_UNION:
2592 if (dty == TY_STRUCT)
2593 appendstring1("struct");
2594 if (dty == TY_UNION)
2595 appendstring1("union");
2596 DTySet(dtype, -dty);
2597 if (DTyAlgTyTag(dtype)) {
2598 appendstring1(" ");
2599 appendsym1(DTyAlgTyTag(dtype));
2600 }
2601 if (DTyAlgTyTag(dtype) == SPTR_NULL || structdepth == 0) {
2602 appendstring1("{");
2603 if (DTyAlgTyMember(dtype)) {
2604 int member;
2605 for (member = DTyAlgTyMember(dtype); member > NOSYM && member < stb.stg_avail;) {
2606 _putdtype(DTYPEG(member), structdepth + 1);
2607 appendstring1(" ");
2608 appendsym1(member);
2609 member = SYMLKG(member);
2610 appendstring1(";");
2611 }
2612 }
2613 appendstring1("}");
2614 }
2615 DTySet(dtype, dty);
2616 break;
2617 case -TY_STRUCT:
2618 case -TY_UNION:
2619 if (dty == -TY_STRUCT)
2620 appendstring1("struct");
2621 if (dty == -TY_UNION)
2622 appendstring1("union");
2623 if (DTyAlgTyTagNeg(dtype)) {
2624 appendstring1(" ");
2625 appendsym1(DTyAlgTyTagNeg(dtype));
2626 } else {
2627 appendstring1(" ");
2628 appendint1(dtype);
2629 }
2630 break;
2631 }
2632
2633} /* _putdtype */
2634
2635void

2637{
2638 _putdtype(dtype, 0);
2639} /* putdtype */

2765 ad = AD_DPTR(dtype);
2766 numdim = AD_NUMDIM(ad);
2767 putint("numdim", numdim);
2768 putnzint("scheck", AD_SCHECK(ad));
2769 putnsym("zbase", (SPTR) AD_ZBASE(ad)); // ???
2770 putnsym("numelm", AD_NUMELM(ad));
2771 putnsym("sdsc", AD_SDSC(ad));
2772 if (numdim >= 1 && numdim <= 7) {
2773 int i;
2774 for (i = 0; i < numdim; ++i) {
2775 putline();
2776 putint("dim", i);
2777 putint("mlpyr", AD_MLPYR(ad, i));
2778 putint("lwbd", AD_LWBD(ad, i));
2779 putint("upbd", AD_UPBD(ad, i));
2780 }
2781 }
2782 break;
2783 case TY_CHAR:
2784 putint("len", DTyCharLength(dtype));
2785 break;
2786 case TY_PARAM:
2787 putint("dtype", DTyArgType(dtype));
2788 putnsym("sptr", DTyArgSym(dtype));
2789 putint("next", DTyArgNext(dtype));
2790 break;
2791 case TY_PTR:
2792 putint("dtype", DTySeqTyElement(dtype));
2793 break;
2794 case TY_STRUCT:
2795 case TY_UNION:
2796 putsym("member", DTyAlgTyMember(dtype));
2797 putint("size", DTyAlgTySize(dtype));
2798 putnsym("tag", DTyAlgTyTag(dtype));
2799 putint("align", DTyAlgTyAlign(dtype));
2800 break;
2801 case TY_VECT:
2802 fprintf(dfile, "<%lu x ", DTyVecLength(dtype));
2803 putdtype(DTySeqTyElement(dtype));
2804 fputc('>', dfile);
2805 FLANG_FALLTHROUGH;
2806 default:
2807 /* simple datatypes, just the one line of info */
2808 putline();
2809 return;
2810 }
2811 putline();
2812 putdtype(dtype);
2813 putline();
2814} /* dumpdtype */

3542 if (ENDSCOPEG(label)) {
3543 appendstring1(" endscope(");
3544 appendsym1(ENCLFUNCG(label));
3545 appendstring1(")");
3546 }
3547 break;
3548 }
3549
3550 case IL_NULL:
3551 if (noprs == 1 && ILI_OPND(i, 1) == 0) {
3552 /* expected case, print nothing else */
3553 appendstring1("NULL");
3554 break;
3555 }
3556 FLANG_FALLTHROUGH;
3557 default:
3558 appendstring1(ilis[opc].name);
3559 if (noprs) {
3560 int j;
3561 appendstring1("(");
3562 for (j = 1; j <= noprs; ++j) {
3563 if (j > 1)
3564 appendstring1(",");
3565 switch (IL_OPRFLAG(opc, j)) {
3566#ifdef ILIO_NULL
3567 case ILIO_NULL:
3568 appendstring1("null=");
3569 appendint1(ILI_OPND(i, j));
3570 break;
3571#endif
3572#ifdef ILIO_SYM
3573 case ILIO_SYM:
3574 if (full) {
3575 appendint1(ILI_OPND(i, j));
3576 appendstring1("=");
3577 }
3578 appendsym1(ILI_OPND(i, j));
3579 break;
3580#endif
3581#ifdef ILIO_OFF
3582 case ILIO_OFF:
3583 appendstring1("off=");
3584 appendint1(ILI_OPND(i, j));
3585 break;
3586#endif
3587#ifdef ILIO_NME
3588 case ILIO_NME:
3589 appendstring1("nme=");
3590 if (full) {
3591 appendint1(ILI_OPND(i, j));
3592 appendstring1("=");
3593 }
3594 _printnme(ILI_OPND(i, j));
3595 break;
3596#endif
3597#ifdef ILIO_IR
3598 case ILIO_IR:
3599 appendstring1("ir=");
3600 appendint1(ILI_OPND(i, j));
3601 break;
3602#endif
3603#ifdef ILIO_SP
3604 case ILIO_SP:
3605 appendstring1("sp=");
3606 appendint1(ILI_OPND(i, j));
3607 break;
3608#endif
3609#ifdef ILIO_DR
3610 case ILIO_DR:
3611 appendstring1("dr=");
3612 appendint1(ILI_OPND(i, j));
3613 break;
3614#endif
3615#ifdef ILIO_AR
3616 case ILIO_AR:
3617 appendstring1("ar=");
3618 appendint1(ILI_OPND(i, j));
3619 break;
3620#endif
3621#ifdef ILIO_KR
3622 case ILIO_KR:
3623 appendstring1("kr=");
3624 appendint1(ILI_OPND(i, j));
3625 break;
3626#endif
3627#ifdef ILIO_XMM
3628 case ILIO_XMM:
3629 /*
3630 bits 0:23 of the operand represent the virtual register
3631 number, and the value of the top byte is 1 for 'ymm'
3632 register, otherwise for 'xmm' register.
3633 */
3634 if (ILI_OPND(i, j) >> 24 == 1)
3635 appendstring1("ymm=");

3641#ifdef ILIO_LNK

3643#endif
3644#ifdef ILIO_IRLNK
3645 case ILIO_IRLNK:
3646#endif
3647#ifdef ILIO_SPLNK
3648 case ILIO_SPLNK:
3649#endif
3650#ifdef ILIO_DPLNK
3651 case ILIO_DPLNK:
3652#endif
3653#ifdef ILIO_ARLNK
3654 case ILIO_ARLNK:
3655#endif
3656#ifdef ILIO_KRLNK
3657 case ILIO_KRLNK:
3658#endif
3659#ifdef ILIO_CSLNK
3660 case ILIO_CSLNK:
3661#endif

3663 case ILIO_CDLNK:
3664#endif
3665#ifdef ILIO_QPLNK
3666 case ILIO_QPLNK:

3672 case ILIO_128LNK:

3674#ifdef ILIO_256LNK
3675 case ILIO_256LNK:
3676#endif
3677#ifdef ILIO_512LNK
3678 case ILIO_512LNK:
3679#endif
3680#ifdef ILIO_X87LNK
3681 case ILIO_X87LNK:

3683#ifdef ILIO_DOUBLEDOUBLELNK

3687 break;
3688 default:
3689 appendstring1("op=");
3690 appendint1(ILI_OPND(i, j));
3691 break;
3692 }
3693 }
3694 appendstring1(")");
3695 }
3696 break;
3697 }
3698
3699 switch (typ) {
3700 case BINOP:
3701 o = optype(ILI_OPC(ILI_OPND(i, 1)));
3702 if (o != OT_UNARY && o != OT_LEAF) {
3703 appendstring1("(");
3704 _printili(ILI_OPND(i, 1));
3705 appendstring1(")");
3706 } else {
3707 _printili(ILI_OPND(i, 1));
3708 }
3709 appendstring1(opval);
3710 o = optype(ILI_OPC(ILI_OPND(i, 2)));
3711 if (o != OT_UNARY && o != OT_LEAF) {
3712 appendstring1("(");
3713 _printili(ILI_OPND(i, 2));
3714 appendstring1(")");
3715 } else {
3716 _printili(ILI_OPND(i, 2));
3717 }
3718 break;
3719 case UNOP:
3720 appendstring1(opval);
3721 o = optype(ILI_OPC(ILI_OPND(i, 1)));
3722 if (o != OT_UNARY && o != OT_LEAF) {
3723 appendstring1("(");
3724 _printili(ILI_OPND(i, 1));
3725 appendstring1(")");
3726 } else {
3727 _printili(ILI_OPND(i, 1));
3728 }
3729 break;
3730 case postUNOP:

3732 if (o != OT_UNARY && o != OT_LEAF) {
3733 appendstring1("(");
3734 _printili(ILI_OPND(i, 1));
3735 appendstring1(")");
3736 } else {
3737 _printili(ILI_OPND(i, 1));
3738 }
3739 appendstring1(opval);
3740 break;
3741 case INTRINSIC:
3742 appendstring1(opval);
3743 appendstring1("(");
3744 for (j = 1; j <= n; ++j) {
3745 _printili(ILI_OPND(i, j));

3747 appendstring1(",");
3748 }
3749 appendstring1(")");
3750 break;
3751 case MVREG:
3752 appendstring1(opval);
3753 appendstring1(".");
3754 appendint1(ILI_OPND(i, 2));

3756 _printili(ILI_OPND(i, 1));
3757 break;
3758 case DFREG:
3759 appendstring1(opval);

3761 appendint1(ILI_OPND(i, 1));
3762 appendstring1(")");
3763 break;
3764 case PSCOMM:
3765 appendstring1(opval);
3766 appendstring1(" = ");
3767 _printili(ILI_OPND(i, 1));
3768 appendstring1(";");
3769 break;
3770 case ENC_N_OP:
3771 appendstring1(opval);
3772 appendstring1("#0x");
3773 appendhex1(ILI_OPND(i, n + 1));
3774 appendstring1("(");
3775 for (j = 1; j <= n; ++j) {
3776 _printili(ILI_OPND(i, j));
3777 if (j != n)
3778 appendstring1(",");
3779 }
3780 appendstring1(")");
3781 break;
3782 default:
3783 break;
3784 }

3919 block = BIHNUMG(GBL_CURRFUNC);

3922 break;

3928 printblock(block);
3929 if (BIH_LAST(block) || block == lastblock)
3930 break;
3931 fprintf(dfile, "\n");
3932 }
3933 if (block != lastblock)
3934 fprintf(dfile, "block:%d not found\n", lastblock);
3935 } else {
3936 for (b = 0; block && b < limit; block = BIH_NEXT(block), ++b) {
3937 printblock(block);
3938 if (BIH_LAST(block) || block == lastblock)
3939 break;
3940 fprintf(dfile, "\n");
3941 }
3942 if (block != lastblock)
3943 fprintf(dfile, "block:%d not found\n", lastblock);
3944 }

4191static void
4192dilitreex(int ilix, int l, int notlast)
4193{
4194 ILI_OP opc;
4195 int noprs, j, jj, nlinks;
4196 int nshift = 0;
4197
4198 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
4199 fprintf(dfile, "%s", prefix);
4200 dili(ilix);
4201 if (ilix <= 0 || ilix >= ilib.stg_size)
4202 return;
4203 if (l) {
4204 if (notlast) {
4205 strcpy(prefix + l - 4, "| ");
4206 } else {
4207 strcpy(prefix + l - 4, " ");
4208 }
4209 }
4210 opc = ILI_OPC(ilix);
4211 if (opc >= 0 && opc < N_ILI) {
4212 noprs = IL_OPRS(opc);
4213 } else {
4214 noprs = 0;
4215 }
4216 nlinks = 0;
4217 for (j = 1; j <= noprs; ++j) {
4218 if (IL_ISLINK(opc, j)) {
4219 ++nlinks;
4220 }
4221 }
4222 if (ILI_ALT(ilix))
4223 ++nlinks;
4224 switch (opc) {
4225 case IL_CSEIR:
4226 case IL_CSESP:
4227 case IL_CSEDP:
4228#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
4229 case IL_CSEQP:
4230#endif
4231 case IL_CSECS:
4232 case IL_CSECD:
4233 case IL_CSEAR:
4234 case IL_CSEKR:
4235 case IL_CSE:
4236#ifdef LONG_DOUBLE_FLOAT128
4237 case IL_FLOAT128CSE:
4238#endif
4239 /* don't recurse unless we're at the top level */
4240 if (l > 4)
4241 nlinks = 0;
4242 break;
4243 case IL_ACCCOPY:
4244 case IL_ACCCOPYIN:
4245 case IL_ACCCOPYOUT:
4246 case IL_ACCLOCAL:
4247 case IL_ACCCREATE:
4248 case IL_ACCDELETE:
4249 case IL_ACCPRESENT:
4250 case IL_ACCPCOPY:
4251 case IL_ACCPCOPYIN:
4252 case IL_ACCPCOPYOUT:
4253 case IL_ACCPCREATE:
4254 case IL_ACCPNOT:
4255 case IL_ACCTRIPLE:
4256 nshift = 1;
4257 break;
4258 default :
4259 break;
4260 }
4261 if (nlinks) {
4262 for (jj = 1; jj <= noprs; ++jj) {
4263 j = jj;
4264 if (nshift) {
4265 j += nshift;
4266 if (j > noprs)
4267 j -= noprs;
4268 }
4269 if (IL_ISLINK(opc, j)) {
4270 int opnd;
4271 opnd = ILI_OPND(ilix, j);
4272 if (ILI_OPC(opnd) != IL_NULL) {
4273 strcpy(prefix + l, "+-- ");

4275 }

4277 }

4280 ILI_OPC(ILI_ALT(ilix)) != IL_NULL) {
4281 int opnd;
4282 opnd = ILI_ALT(ilix);
4283 strcpy(prefix + l, "+-- ");
4284 dilitreex(opnd, l + 4, --nlinks);
4285 prefix[l] = '\0';
4286 }
4287 }

4673static void
4674_printnme(int n)
4675{
4676 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
4677 if (n < 0 || n >= nmeb.stg_avail) {
4678 putint("nme", n);
4679 return;
4680 }
4681 switch (NME_TYPE(n)) {
4682 case NT_VAR:
4683 appendstring1(printname(NME_SYM(n)));
4684 if (NME_SYM(n) > NOSYM && NME_SYM(n) < stb.stg_avail &&
4685 SCG(NME_SYM(n)) == SC_PRIVATE)
4686 appendstring1("'");
4687 break;
4688 case NT_MEM:
4689 if (NME_NM(n)) {
4690 _printnme(NME_NM(n));
4691 } else {
4692 appendstring1("Unknown");
4693 }
4694 if (NME_SYM(n) == 0) {
4695 appendstring1(".real");
4696 } else if (NME_SYM(n) == 1) {
4697 appendstring1(".imag");
4698 } else {
4699 appendstring1(".");
4700 appendstring1(printname(NME_SYM(n)));
4701 }
4702 break;
4703 case NT_ARR:
4704 if (NME_NM(n)) {
4705 _printnme(NME_NM(n));
4706 } else {
4707 appendstring1("Unknown");
4708 }
4709 if (NME_SYM(n) == 0) {
4710 appendstring1("[");
4711 appendint1(NME_CNST(n));
4712 appendstring1("]");
4713 } else if (NME_SUB(n) != 0) {
4714 appendstring1("[");
4715 _printili(NME_SUB(n));
4716 appendstring1("]");
4717 } else {
4718 appendstring1("[?]");
4719 }
4720 break;
4721 case NT_IND:
4722 appendstring1("*(");
4723 if (NME_NM(n)) {
4724 _printnme(NME_NM(n));
4725 } else {
4726 appendstring1("Unknown");
4727 }
4728 if (NME_SYM(n) == NME_NULL) {
4729 } else if (NME_SYM(n) == 0) {
4730 if (NME_CNST(n)) {
4731 appendstring1("+");
4732 appendint1(NME_CNST(n));
4733 }
4734 } else {
4735 appendstring1("+?");
4736 }
4737 appendstring1(")");
4738 if (NME_SUB(n) != 0) {
4739 appendstring1("[");
4740 _printili(NME_SUB(n));
4741 appendstring1("]");
4742 }
4743 break;
4744 case NT_UNK:
4745 if (NME_SYM(n) == 0) {
4746 appendstring1("unknown");
4747 } else if (NME_SYM(n) == 1) {
4748 appendstring1("volatile");
4749 } else {
4750 appendstring1("unknown:");
4751 appendint1(NME_SYM(n));
4752 }
4753 break;
4754 default:
4755 appendstring1("nme(");
4756 appendint1(n);
4757 appendstring1(":");
4758 appendint1(NME_TYPE(n));
4759 appendstring1(")");
4760 break;
4761 }
4762} /* _printnme */

4780static const char *nmetypes[] = {"unknown ", "indirect", "variable",
4781 "member ", "element ", "safe "};
4782
4783void
4784_dumpnme(int n, bool dumpdefsuses)
4785{
4786 int pte;
4787 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
4788 if (n <= 0 || n >= nmeb.stg_avail) {
4789 fprintf(dfile, "\nNME %d out of %d\n", n, nmeb.stg_avail - 1);
4790 return;
4791 }
4792 if (nmeb.stg_base == NULL) {
4793 fprintf(dfile, "nmeb.stg_base not allocated\n");
4794 return;
4795 }
4796 if (full) {
4797 putint("nme", n);
4798 } else {
4799 putstring1("nme");
4800 }
4801 putval1(NME_TYPE(n), nmetypes, SIZEOF(nmetypes));
4802 switch (NME_TYPE(n)) {
4803 case NT_VAR:
4804 putsym("var", NME_SYM(n));
4805 break;
4806 case NT_MEM:
4807 pprintnme(n);
4808 if (NME_SYM(n) == 0) {
4809 putstring1(".real");
4810 } else if (NME_SYM(n) == 1) {
4811 putstring1(".imag");
4812 break;
4813 } else {
4814 putsym("member", NME_SYM(n));
4815 }
4816 break;
4817 case NT_ARR:
4818 case NT_IND:
4819 pprintnme(n);
4820 if (NME_SYM(n) == NME_NULL) {
4821 putint("sym", -1);
4822 } else if (NME_SYM(n) == 0) {
4823 } else {
4824 if (NME_SYM(n) > 0 && NME_SYM(n) < stb.stg_avail) {
4825 putsym("sym", NME_SYM(n));
4826 } else {
4827 putnzint("sym", NME_SYM(n));
4828 }
4829 }
4830 break;
4831 case NT_UNK:
4832 pprintnme(n);
4833 break;
4834 default:
4835 if (NME_SYM(n) > 0 && NME_SYM(n) < stb.stg_avail) {
4836 putsym("sym", NME_SYM(n));
4837 } else {
4838 putnzint("sym", NME_SYM(n));
4839 }
4840 break;
4841 }
4842 putnzint("nm", NME_NM(n));
4843#ifdef NME_BASE
4844 putnzint("base", NME_BASE(n));
4845#endif
4846 putnzint("cnst", NME_CNST(n));
4847 putnzint("cnt", NME_CNT(n));
4848 if (full & 1)
4849 putnzint("hashlink", NME_HSHLNK(n));
4850 putnzint("inlarr", NME_INLARR(n));
4851 putnzint("rat/rfptr", NME_RAT(n));
4852 putnzint("stl", NME_STL(n));
4853 putnzint("sub", NME_SUB(n));
4854 putnzint("mask", NME_MASK(n));
4855#ifdef NME_PTE
4856 pte = NME_PTE(n);
4857 if (dumpdefsuses && pte) {
4858 putline();
4859 putstring1("pointer targets:");
4860 putptelist(pte);
4861 }
4862#endif
4863} /* _dumpnme */

4900char *
4901printname(int sptr)
4902{
4903 extern void cprintf(char *s, const char *format, INT *val);
4904 static char b[200];
4905 double dd;
4906 union {
4907 float ff;
4908 ISZ_T ww;
4909 } xx;
4910
4911 if (sptr <= 0 || sptr >= stb.stg_avail) {
4912 snprintf(b, 200, "symbol %d out of %d", sptr, stb.stg_avail - 1);
4913 return b;
4914 }
4915
4916 if (STYPEG(sptr) == ST_CONST) {
4917 INT num[2], cons1, cons2;
4918 int pointee;
4919 char *bb, *ee;
4920 switch (DTY(DTYPEG(sptr))) {
4921 case TY_INT8:
4922 case TY_UINT8:
4923 num[0] = CONVAL1G(sptr);
4924 num[1] = CONVAL2G(sptr);
4925 ui64toax(num, b, 22, 0, 10);
4926 break;
4927 case TY_INT:
4928 snprintf(b, 200, "%10d", CONVAL2G(sptr));
4929 break;
4930
4931 case TY_FLOAT:
4932 xx.ww = CONVAL2G(sptr);
4933 if ((xx.ww & 0x7f800000) == 0x7f800000) {
4934 /* Infinity or NaN */
4935 snprintf(b, 200, ("(float)(0x%8.8" ISZ_PF "x)"), xx.ww);
4936 } else {
4937 dd = xx.ff;
4938 snprintf(b, 200, "%.8ef", dd);
4939 }
4940 break;
4941
4942 case TY_DBLE:
4943 num[0] = CONVAL1G(sptr);
4944 num[1] = CONVAL2G(sptr);
4945 if ((num[0] & 0x7ff00000) == 0x7ff00000) {
4946 /* Infinity or NaN */
4947 snprintf(b, 200, "(double)(0x%8.8x%8.8xLL)", num[0], num[1]);
4948 } else {
4949 cprintf(b, "%.17le", num);
4950 }
4951 break;
4952
4953 case TY_CMPLX:
4954 xx.ww = CONVAL1G(sptr);
4955 if ((xx.ww & 0x7f800000) == 0x7f800000) {
4956 /* Infinity or NaN */
4957 int len;
4958 len = snprintf(b, 200, ("(0x%8.8" ISZ_PF "x, "), xx.ww);
4959 bb = b + len;
4960 } else {
4961 b[0] = '(';
4962 sprintf(&b[1], "%17.10e", xx.ff);
4963 b[18] = ',';
4964 b[19] = ' ';
4965 bb = &b[20];
4966 }
4967 xx.ww = CONVAL2G(sptr);
4968 if ((xx.ww & 0x7f800000) == 0x7f800000) {
4969 snprintf(bb, 200, ("(0x%8.8" ISZ_PF "x, "), xx.ww);
4970 } else {
4971 sprintf(bb, "%17.10e", xx.ff);
4972 bb += 17;
4973 *bb++ = ')';
4974 *bb = '\0';
4975 }
4976 break;
4977
4978 case TY_DCMPLX:
4979 cons1 = CONVAL1G(sptr);
4980 cons2 = CONVAL2G(sptr);
4981 num[0] = CONVAL1G(cons1);
4982 num[1] = CONVAL2G(cons1);
4983 if ((num[0] & 0x7ff00000) == 0x7ff00000) {
4984 /* Infinity or NaN */
4985 int len;
4986 len = snprintf(b, 200, "(0x%8.8x%8.8xLL, ", num[0], num[1]);
4987 bb = b + len;
4988
4989 } else {
4990 b[0] = '(';
4991 cprintf(&b[1], "%24.17le", num);
4992 b[25] = ',';
4993 b[26] = ' ';
4994 bb = &b[27];
4995 }
4996
4997 num[0] = CONVAL1G(cons2);
4998 num[1] = CONVAL2G(cons2);
4999 if ((num[0] & 0x7ff00000) == 0x7ff00000) {
5000 /* Infinity or NaN */
5001 snprintf(bb, 200, "0x%8.8x%8.8xLL", num[0], num[1]);
5002 } else {
5003 cprintf(bb, "%24.17le", num);
5004 bb += 24;
5005 *bb++ = ')';
5006 *bb = '\0';
5007 }
5008
5009 break;
5010
5011 case TY_QUAD:
5012 num[0] = CONVAL1G(sptr);
5013 num[1] = CONVAL2G(sptr);
5014 cprintf(b, "%.17le", num);
5015 break;
5016
5017 case TY_PTR:
5018 pointee = CONVAL1G(sptr);
5019 if (pointee > 0 && pointee < stb.stg_avail && STYPEG(pointee) != ST_CONST
5020 ) {
5021 if (ACONOFFG(sptr) == 0) {
5022 snprintf(b, 200, "*%s", SYMNAME(pointee));
5023 } else {
5024 snprintf(b, 200, "*%s+%" ISZ_PF "d", SYMNAME(pointee),
5025 ACONOFFG(sptr));
5026 }
5027 } else {
5028 if (ACONOFFG(sptr) == 0) {
5029 snprintf(b, 200, "*(sym %d)", pointee);
5030 } else {
5031 snprintf(b, 200, "*(sym %d)+%" ISZ_PF "d", pointee, ACONOFFG(sptr));
5032 }
5033 }
5034 break;
5035
5036 case TY_WORD:
5037 snprintf(b, 200, "%10" ISZ_PF "d", ACONOFFG(sptr));
5038 break;
5039
5040 case TY_CHAR:
5041 return stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(sptr);
5042 case TY_BLOG:
5043 case TY_SLOG:
5044 case TY_LOG:
5045 snprintf(b, 200, "%10d", CONVAL2G(sptr));
5046 break;
5047 case TY_LOG8:
5048 num[0] = CONVAL1G(sptr);
5049 num[1] = CONVAL2G(sptr);
5050 ui64toax(num, b, 22, 0, 10);
5051 break;
5052
5053 default:
5054 snprintf(b, 200, "unknown constant %d dty %d", sptr,
5055 DTY(DTYPEG(sptr)));
5056 break;
5057 }
5058 for (bb = b; *bb == ' '; ++bb)
5059 ;
5060 for (ee = bb; *ee; ++ee)
5061 ; /* go to end of string */
5062 for (; ee > bb && *(ee - 1) == ' '; --ee)
5063 *ee = '\0';
5064 return bb;
5065 }
5066 /* default case */
5067 if (strncmp(SYMNAME(sptr), "..inline", 8) == 0) {
5068 /* append symbol number to distinguish */
5069 snprintf(b, 200, "%s_%d", SYMNAME(sptr), sptr);
5070 return b;
5071 }
5072 return SYMNAME(sptr);
5073} /* printname */

5127/*
5128 * diagnose what stack locations are used
5129 */
5130void
5131stackcheck()
5132{
5133 long maxstack, minstack, i, j, addr, size, totused, totfree;
5134 int sptr, lastclash;
5135 int *stack, *stackmem;
5136 dfile = gbl.dbgfil ? gbl.dbgfil : stderr;
5137 minstack = 0;
5138 maxstack = -1;
5139 for (sptr = gbl.locals; sptr > NOSYM; sptr = SYMLKG(sptr)) {
5140 size = size_of(DTYPEG(sptr));
5141 if (ADDRESSG(sptr) - size < minstack)
5142 minstack = ADDRESSG(sptr) - size;
5143 if (ADDRESSG(sptr) + size > maxstack)
5144 maxstack = ADDRESSG(sptr) + size;
5145 }
5146 fprintf(dfile, "Stack for subprogram %d:%s\n%8ld:%-8ld\n", gbl.func_count,
5147 SYMNAME(gbl.currsub), minstack, maxstack);
5148 stackmem = (int *)malloc((maxstack - minstack + 1) * sizeof(int));
5149 stack = stackmem - minstack; /* minstack is <= 0 */
5150 for (i = minstack; i <= maxstack; ++i)
5151 stack[i] = 0;
5152 for (sptr = gbl.locals; sptr > NOSYM; sptr = SYMLKG(sptr)) {
5153 addr = ADDRESSG(sptr);
5154 size = size_of(DTYPEG(sptr));
5155 lastclash = 0;
5156 for (i = addr; i < addr + size; ++i) {
5157 if (stack[i] != 0) {
5158 if (stack[i] != lastclash)
5159 fprintf(dfile, "sptr %d:%s and %d:%s clash at memory %ld\n", sptr,
5160 SYMNAME(sptr), stack[i], SYMNAME(stack[i]), i);
5161 lastclash = stack[i];
5162 }
5163 stack[i] = sptr;
5164 }
5165 }
5166 sptr = -1;
5167 totfree = 0;
5168 totused = 0;
5169 for (i = minstack; i <= maxstack; ++i) {
5170 if (stack[i] == 0)
5171 ++totfree;
5172 else
5173 ++totused;
5174 if (stack[i] != sptr) {
5175 sptr = stack[i];
5176 for (j = i; j < maxstack && stack[j + 1] == sptr; ++j)
5177 ;
5178 if (sptr == 0) {
5179 fprintf(dfile, "%8ld:%-8ld ---free (%ld)\n", i, j, j - i + 1);
5180 } else {
5181 size = size_of(DTYPEG(sptr));
5182 fprintf(dfile, "%8ld:%-8ld %8ld(%%rsp) %5d:%s (%ld) ", i, j,
5183 i + 8 - minstack, sptr, SYMNAME(sptr), size);
5184 putdtypex(DTYPEG(sptr), 1000);
5185 fprintf(dfile, "\n");
5186 }
5187 }
5188 }
5189 fprintf(dfile, "%8ld used\n%8ld free\n", totused, totfree);
5190 free(stackmem);
5191} /* stackcheck */
